Name: LAETUS.
About the game: LAETUS. is a rapid 2D precision platformer focused on speed and skill. You play as a small yet swift circle racing against the developer for the fastest time. Speed your way through challenging levels and use all aspects of your movement and colour-changing abilities to finish in record time! (Hint: Intended ways aren't always the fastest...)
